## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="473b6-159">L'esempio di codice seguente Reimposta la trasformazione geometrica di `pgBrush` all'identità.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="473b6-159">The following code example resets the geometric transform of `pgBrush` to identity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="473b6-160">Si presuppone che `myPath` è presente alcuna <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="473b6-160">It is assumed that `myPath` is an existing <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>.</span></span>  
  
